reviewText:
AMAZON has such a variety and the prices are very competitive.

DO a cart full of stuff at your usual and then re-do it on AMAZON.

Worth a try isn't it?

I found this video extremely helpful as part of my research on both the 95th Rifles and the Peninsular War. The only thing better would be to visit the battlefields in person. Seeing the part played by the Rifles was a definite asset.
